</div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">限制您的文件历史被追踪的时间长度</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">文件历史和回收站</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">文件历史和回收站</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">确保<span class="gui">文件历史</span>开关已设置为开启状态。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">在<span class="gui">文件历史持续时间</span>下，选择保留文件历史的时间。可以从<span class="gui">1天</span>、<span class="gui">7天</span>、<span class="gui">30天</span>或<span class="gui">永久</span>等选项中选择。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">使用<span class="gui">清除历史…</span>按钮可立即清除历史记录。</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
